<br>
Additionnally, secondary stats (WS and Hit points) do not recalculate correctly when you respec. You need to force them to reset for that (best way is to unequip/equip something, although loging/zoning works.<br>
<br>
For the new shouts, the lvl 43 lvl one is an upgrade of the lvl 35. And the lvl 50 one an upgrade of the lvl 44.<br>
Which means : At 43 BS : 26/43 shouts<br>
                    At 44 BS : 43/44 shouts<br>
                    At 50 BS : 43/50 shouts.<br>
<br>
The usefulness of the 50 weapon/43 BS template drops sharply. But 49/44 is competitive, especially for trolls (And Axe best style is Artic Rift at 44 anyway). 5 more spec in weapon is probably around 100-150 WS fully buffed for a Troll.<br>
<br>
Remember that the higher the DD, the less power efficient it is. For people with 50 BS, MCL will probably be a must, but a 44 or 46 BS skald can spend the points somewhere else.<br>
<br>
Considering 47 to 50 brings nothing of interest but that shout, I'm not convinced 50 Bs is the best option.<br>
